Package: gitflower
Architecture: all
Depends: ${python3:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, git, adduser
Description: git-based development platform
 gitflower provides a local-first, git-centric development platform:
 per-repository branch workflow enforcement via a pre-receive hook engine
 (protected branches, allow-listed branch rules, linear-history and
 clean-tree checks) and a lightweight web UI for browsing hosted bare
 repositories — tree, blob and commit views, a commit-graph
 visualization, and read-only git smart-HTTP cloning.
 .
 The web API is also the frontend: every endpoint serves JSON, a full
 HTML page, and an HTML fragment from the same URL through content
 negotiation.
